       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING  AREA-LINK-NOMINA.
       DECLARATIVES.
               COPY "..\DCL\AUDITE.DCL".
               COPY "..\DCL\TARIESGO.DCL".
               COPY "..\DCL\FRIESGOS.DCL".
               COPY "..\DCL\USER-ACT.DCL".
